before(pt.iscte.dcti.qualifiers.AccessibleFrom): accessToNonPrivateAccessibleFromAnnotatedField..

AdviceType: Before

Scope: Accesses to non private attributes annotated with @AccessibleFrom.

Name: nonPrivateAttributesAccessEnforcer

This advice verifies if the annotated private attributes are accessed by an allowed class. Just the class itself and its specializations have access and if the accessor class doesn't belong to the annotation's given set of classes the access is restricted and an exception thrown. @throws IllegalAccess if the accessor class has restricted access.
